      "date": "2014-06-09 13:01:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(2 comments)\n\n3 style warning(s).\nFor more details please see https://wiki.hpdd.intel.com/display/PUB/Coding+Guidelines",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
